CBRE is pleased to offer 10 Cato Street, Hawthorn East for sale by Expressions of Interest closing Thursday 17th of June at 12noon. 

Situated on the southern side of Cato Street with vast 20m* frontage and lane way access, development applications (STCA) will benefit from good natural light and precinct views.

Key benefits of this outstanding offering include:
+  Vacant land parcel of 1,124sqm* currently utilised as a car park.
+  Frontage of  20 metres to Cato Street with rear access from Cato Lane.
+  Flexible Commercial 2 Zone, with potential to develop up to six (6) levels (STCA).

Situated in the heart of the affluent Boroondara Municipality the property occupies a prominent location seconds from the Monash Freeway and within walking distance to Tooronga Village Shopping Centre and Tooronga Train Station.

10 Cato Street is being offered for sale with 8 Cato Street, Hawthorn East with the properties being able to be purchased together or separately.
